{"tid":1095282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[腦魔]裁員1600人平均37歲？ Oracle中國驚傳將關閉研發中心","createTime":"2019-04-07T02:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T16:13:54.000Z","uid":54733,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1cb3f79be8d93755b63bf94907dd13c92950f027","tid":1095282,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T02:18:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinacn10116/40/w530h310/20190406/a8e2-hvhrcxm3768471.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fsinacn10116%2F40%2Fw530h310%2F20190406%2Fa8e2-hvhrcxm3768471.jpg&h=fb8e6ff0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日，有媒體收到來自Oracle甲骨文中國內部員工的消息，Oracle 中國研發中心或徹底關閉，涉及約 1600 名工程師的命運。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，裁員已確定第一階段約 500 人，其中包括雲計算部門的 130～190 人。但目前均未收到人力資源部門的正式通知。<br />\n<br />\n和其他外企一樣，Oracle中國研發中心工程師年齡平均在 37 歲左右，此次被裁之後面臨找新工作和生活的巨大壓力。<br />\n<br />\n3月23日，Oracle執行副總裁Don Johnson發送了一封標題為&ldquo;組織重組&rdquo;的電子郵件。該郵件告知工作人員：將來，公司的一切工作都將圍繞Oracle雲基礎設施（OCI）業務展開。今天OCI內部的變化與拉里?埃利森的公司願景更保持一致。它將簡化我們的產品和服務，將投資重心放在我們最具戰略意義的優先事項上，並幫助我們更高效、更快速地兌現Oracle第二代云的全部承諾和覆蓋範圍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.cj.sina.com.cn/articles/view/6586475408/18895a39000100g386\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.cj.sina.com.cn%2Farticles%2Fview%2F6586475408%2F18895a39000100g386&d=bZmkWp0iUYBi2b5pBzw%2FEcTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=45abeea0\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.cj.sina.com.cn/articles/view/6586475408/18895a39000100g386</a>"},{"pid":"aae840ee58a5c98631f7b3460b9075555be18ba1","tid":1095282,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T02:19:55.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"e2afdb6b163a4e6e08e54fb6b62102a4cdc68fcc","tid":1095282,"uid":58413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T02:29:42.000Z","msg":"37其實好搶手"},{"pid":"2203f9b6dc0670fdf2a72261bcc5eae796d0ec39","tid":1095282,"uid":22535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T02:31:22.000Z","msg":"唔想再畀支那人偷技術<img